ActAccess to Information Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Access to Information Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the ACCESS TO INFORMATION REGULATIONS (SCHEDULE I) in order to (1) strengthen the capacity of federal departments and agencies to collect and share intelligence with other federal institutions and agencies, and to protect certain information in response to an access request; and (2) modernize administrative practices through existing legistated regimes.
